---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

export const title = "Old Orchard Beach Dispensary Guide";
---

<Layout 
  title="Old Orchard Beach Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in Old Orchard Beach, Maine. Market analysis, regulations, and investment requirements."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Old Orchard Beach Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Old Orchard Beach, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section class="fact-box">
      <h2>📋 Old Orchard Beach at a Glance</h2>
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>License Required</strong></td><td>Maine OCP Adult-Use Retail License</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Local Fee</strong></td><td>$2,000-2,500 annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>School Buffer</strong></td><td>500 ft minimum</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Commercial Rent</strong></td><td>$16-24/sq ft annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Current Dispensaries</strong></td><td>1-2 (opportunity)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why Old Orchard Beach?</h2>
      <p>Old Orchard Beach is a premier tourist destination with 8,000+ year-round residents and 100,000+ summer visitors annually. The summer tourist population creates exceptional seasonal revenue opportunity.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Tourist Season Opportunity" type="passion">
      Old Orchard Beach is THE summer cannabis destination in southern Maine. If you can handle the seasonality, the summer months can generate a full year's revenue. It's a unique market that rewards operators who plan for the boom.
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Data</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Year-Round Pop</td><td>8,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Summer Visitors</td><td>100,000+ (seasonal)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Very Low</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Seasonality</td><td>High (May-Sept)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local X-Factor: The Tourist Premium</h2>
      <p><strong>What sets OOB apart:</strong> Summer tourists—many from states without legal cannabis—eagerly visit Maine dispensaries. They pay premium prices without comparison shopping.</p>
      <p><strong>Strategic Implication:</strong> Stock premium products. Tourist customers prioritize quality and convenience over price. Plan staffing for July-August peak.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Area</th><th>Pros</th><th>Rent/Sq Ft</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Portland Avenue</strong></td><td>Main tourist drag</td><td>$20-24</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Ocean Park</strong></td><td>Historic area</td><td>$16-20</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Route 1</strong></td><td>Year-round traffic</td><td>$14-18</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>✅ Opportunity:</strong> Tourist premium pricing</li>
        <li><strong>⚠️ Factor:</strong> Heavy seasonality</li>
        <li><strong>💰 Investment:</strong> $300K-400K</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine OCP</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/">License Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Informational only.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .fact-box { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.1); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .fact-box h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box table { margin: 0; }
</style>